{"tid":2157700,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［賠了夫人］如果拜仁拿歐聯，巴塞要付利物浦500萬","createTime":"2020-08-15T08:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T17:19:11.000Z","uid":43785,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"965fd3f5d7489912cf678e1a637c37cf697475d8","tid":2157700,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:07:16.000Z","msg":"輸8球未係最慘，最慘係，因為古天奴份合約，如果拜仁拿歐聯，巴塞要付利物浦500萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條款好似只說明「5年內拿歐聯」，並沒有說明「替巴塞」拿歐聯！<br />\n利記究竟會唔會攞呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都未見過D人咁反骨，入自己果隊兩球都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />報仇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/philippe-coutinho-barcelona-liverpool-transfer-22525250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Fnews%2Fphilippe-coutinho-barcelona-liverpool-transfer-22525250&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8W6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=a4a45859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/philippe-coutinho-barcelona-liverpool-transfer-22525250</a><br />\n<br />\nBTW，<br />\n古天奴以為離開利物浦就有歐聯，點知原來係離開巴塞先有歐聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今年終於有機會了"},{"pid":"477b41dab97b5f5b913d3ae2f0eadee72c1d1455","tid":2157700,"uid":22210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:07:40.000Z","msg":"你點賠的"},{"pid":"acdd930b23953654179186b6a257a7fb0ff75953","tid"